507
00:37:30,760 --> 00:37:32,660
Right.

508
00:38:30,970 --> 00:38:34,570
<i>Fan Xian. Fan Xian.</i>

509
00:38:36,240 --> 00:38:39,980
<i>Fan Xia, are you asleep?</i>

510
00:38:39,980 --> 00:38:42,580
