524
00:39:40,020 --> 00:39:41,830
What do you think?

525
00:39:44,000 --> 00:39:46,110
It's a yes then.

526
00:39:46,110 --> 00:39:48,620
Don't forget about it. Tomorrow at noon.

527
00:39:49,660 --> 00:39:52,700
